### =============================================
### EMPLOYEE ENDPOINTS
### =============================================

### Çalışan Listesi
GET http://localhost:8080/employees
Accept: text/html

###

### Yeni Çalışan Formu
GET http://localhost:8080/employees/new
Accept: text/html

###

### Yeni Çalışan Oluştur (CV olmadan)
POST http://localhost:8080/employees
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

firstName=Ahmet&lastName=Yılmaz&email=ahmet.yilmaz@sirket.com&department=Yazılım&position=Backend Developer&hireDate=2024-01-15

###

### Yeni Çalışan Oluştur (CV ile birlikte)
POST http://localhost:8080/employees
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----FormBoundary

------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="firstName"

Mehmet
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="lastName"

Kaya
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="email"

mehmet.kaya@sirket.com
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="department"

İnsan Kaynakları
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="position"

İK Uzmanı
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="hireDate"

2024-03-01
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="resumeFile"; filename="mehmet-cv.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./test-files/sample-cv.pdf
------FormBoundary--

###

### Çalışan Detayı (id=1)
GET http://localhost:8080/employees/1
Accept: text/html

###

### Çalışan Düzenleme Formu (id=1)
GET http://localhost:8080/employees/1/edit
Accept: text/html

###

### Çalışan Güncelle (id=1)
POST http://localhost:8080/employees/1
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

firstName=Ahmet&lastName=Yılmaz&email=ahmet.updated@sirket.com&department=DevOps&position=Senior Developer&hireDate=2024-01-15

###

### Çalışan Sil (id=1)
POST http://localhost:8080/employees/1/delete

###

### =============================================
### RESUME (CV) ENDPOINTS
### =============================================

### Tüm CV Listesi
GET http://localhost:8080/resumes
Accept: text/html

###

### Çalışana Ait CV Listesi (employeeId=1)
GET http://localhost:8080/employees/1/resumes
Accept: text/html

###

### CV Yükle (employeeId=1)
POST http://localhost:8080/employees/1/resumes/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----CVBoundary

------CVBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test-cv.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./test-files/sample-cv.pdf
------CVBoundary--

###

### CV İndir (resumeId=1)
GET http://localhost:8080/resumes/1/download

###

### CV Sil (resumeId=1, employeeId ile redirect)
POST http://localhost:8080/resumes/1/delete
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

employeeId=1

###
